---
title: Tex-Mex Portobello and Pepper Fajitas with Lime Crema
description: Tender-crisp onions and peppers are paired with meaty portobello mushrooms in these flavour-packed fajitas! Top with a dollop of a refreshing lime crema and you're good to go!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1009_W32_CA_RV152914-3_Main_low-ec7116fc.jpg
